Label: number of employees
Definition: The number of people (headcount) who receive paychecks from the organization for work performed
Editors Note: Informal organizations do not have employees.  Create a class restriction as a domain.

Label: has URL representation
Definition: A URI that represents the address of a web site on the world wide web
Example: The URL of the United Nations home page is http://un.org

Label: has official organization name
Definition: The name of the organization which appears in the current documents authorizing its existence
Example: The official name of the united states is The United States of America.

Label: has organization name
Example: Names of The United States of America incude: USA, US, United States, America.
